Strategy Markup Language (StratML) is an XML vocabulary and schema for strategic plans.  supports StratML Part 1
      (Strategic Plan) and StratML Part 2 (Performance Plans and Reports) and provides templates for
      the following documents:

Strategic Plan (StratML Part 1);

Performance Plan (StratML Part 2);

Performance Report - (StratML Part 2);

Strategic Plan - (StratML Part 2).
